<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>nekoten</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
</head>

<body class="blurBg">
    <!-- loader --> 
    <div class="ui dimmer" id="dimmer">
        <div class="ui massive text loader">
            <h3>Loading</h3>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="wrapper" class="ui text container fadein-animation">
        <div>
          <%= image_tag  "logo.png" %>
        </div>
        <h2>猫の写真がたくさん集まる”猫の天国”</h2>
        <p>お気に入りの猫ごとに写真も管理できて、とってもベンリ<br>猫の天国を覗いてみましょう！</p>
        <div class="top-start-button fadein-animation">
            <%= link_to "start", new_user_session_path, class: 'ui black button' ,id: "topstart" %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>

